➜冬闲变农忙，奏响一曲乡村振兴之歌——米东区“南果北种”基地的丰收色彩
http://www.sohu.com/a/433662586_118570	8768
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201123/a6346cca37f14d87bd9548cc89808e17.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">图①为种植户张建萍（左）正在教游客采摘百香果。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201123/f707f5babfa449848486d00e6bc59274.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">图②为种植户赵建萍查看木瓜长势。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201123/1467a531b25844c78519ab2472315a69.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">图③为火龙果已经成熟。</span></img></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
